{"parse":{"title":"Brooklyn Thrill Killers","pageid":21854195,"revid":837039198,"text":{"*":"<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg/220px-3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"179\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg/330px-3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/6/61/3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg/440px-3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"640\" data-file-height=\"520\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:3_Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_Stenographers_and_DA.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The District Attorney holds up the <a href=\"/wiki/Bullwhip\" title=\"Bullwhip\">bullwhip</a> used by the three boys behind him, in one of the attacks</div></div></div>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:222px;\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg/220px-Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg\" width=\"220\" height=\"148\" class=\"thumbimage\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg/330px-Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/81/Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg/440px-Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg 2x\" data-file-width=\"760\" data-file-height=\"510\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/wiki/File:Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers_with_corpse_of_Willard_Mellard.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>The boys, <a href=\"/wiki/Handcuff\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Handcuff\">handcuffed</a>, alongside the corpse of Willard Mellard</div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>Brooklyn Thrill Killers</b> were a gang of <a href=\"/wiki/Jewish\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Jewish\">Jewish</a> teenage boys who, in the summer of 1954, killed two men (one by drowning, the other by beating) and <a href=\"/wiki/Torture\" title=\"Torture\">tortured</a> several others in <a href=\"/wiki/Brooklyn\" title=\"Brooklyn\">Brooklyn</a>, a <a href=\"/wiki/Borough_(New_York_City)\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Borough (New York City)\">borough</a> of <a href=\"/wiki/New_York_City\" title=\"New York City\">New York City</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-time_dec_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-time_dec-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>The Brooklyn Thrill Killers were:\n</p>\n<ul><li>Robert Trachtenberg</li>\n<li>Jack Koslow</li>\n<li>Melvin Mittman</li>\n<li>Jerome Lieberman</li></ul>\n<p>According to a 1954 article in <i><a href=\"/wiki/Time_Magazine\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Time Magazine\">Time Magazine</a></i>, one of the boys <a href=\"/wiki/Turn_state%27s_evidence\" title=\"Turn state&#39;s evidence\">turned State's evidence</a> and another had the charges against him dismissed.  The other two boys, aged 17 and 18, were found guilty of <a href=\"/wiki/Felony_murder\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Felony murder\">felony murder</a> during the act of kidnapping because one victim had been dragged several blocks before being thrown in the river.  This allowed the jury to suggest <a href=\"/wiki/Life_in_prison\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Life in prison\">life in prison</a> rather than send two youths to the <a href=\"/wiki/Electric_chair\" title=\"Electric chair\">electric chair</a>. While <i>Time</i> didn't identify any of the boys, one of the two sentenced to life in prison was 18-year-old Jack Koslow, identified by <a href=\"/wiki/Associated_Press\" title=\"Associated Press\">AP</a> reports at the time as the 'brains' of the group.\n</p><p>Dr. <a href=\"/wiki/Fredric_Wertham\" title=\"Fredric Wertham\">Fredric Wertham</a> cited the Thrill Killers as an example of the potential harm caused by <a href=\"/wiki/Comic_book\" title=\"Comic book\">comic books</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-:0_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:0-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> Specifically, a comic book named <i><a href=\"/wiki/Nights_of_Horror\" title=\"Nights of Horror\">Nights of Horror</a></i> was brought as evidence of Jack Koslow's \"sexual perversions\", and used to convict him and Mittman of their crimes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-:0_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-:0-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Film\">Film</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Film\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Derek Davidson and Paul Franco wrote and directed a 1999 <a href=\"/wiki/Short_film\" title=\"Short film\">short film</a> about the events surrounding the incident and starring <a href=\"/wiki/Chip_Zien\" title=\"Chip Zien\">Chip Zien</a>, <a href=\"/wiki/Anne_Meara\" title=\"Anne Meara\">Anne Meara</a>, and <a href=\"/wiki/Dan_Fogler\" title=\"Dan Fogler\">Dan Fogler</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"See_also\">See also</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: See also\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li><a href=\"/wiki/Self-hating_Jew\" title=\"Self-hating Jew\">Self-hating Jew</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/w/index.php?title=Brooklyn_Thrill_Killers&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-time_dec-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-time_dec_1-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.time.com/time/magazine/article/0,9171,857873,00.html\">\u201cThrill Killers\u201d,</a> <i>Time</i>, 27 December 1954.</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-:0-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\">^ <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_2-0\"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href=\"#cite_ref-:0_2-1\"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.secret-identity.net\">Secret Identity</a></i> by Craig Yoe, published April 2009</span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://nl.newsbank.com/nl-search/we/Archives?p_product=CO&amp;s_site=charlotte&amp;p_multi=CO&amp;p_theme=realcities&amp;p_action=search&amp;p_maxdocs=200&amp;p_topdoc=1&amp;p_text_direct-0=0EB6D1E7C5F319A8&amp;p_field_direct-0=document_id&amp;p_perpage=10&amp;p_sort=YMD_date:D&amp;s_trackval=GooglePM\">\"MMAVERICK MOGUL INSPIRES FILM FEST\"</a>. <i><a href=\"/wiki/Charlotte_Observ